-- Morgan Stanley must pay $4.5 mln to Citigroup's Banamex unit -panel
-- By Suzanne Barlyn
-- Fri Aug 15, 2014 03:07PM EDT
-- None



Aug 15 (Reuters) - Morgan Stanley & Co Inc must pay $4.5 million to Citigroup's Banamex unit which alleged the firm had allowed funds in a family's trust account to be used to repay third-party loans without its authorization, according to a ruling on Friday.

